  "detailed_description": "Spread a trail of warmth throughout the world in this wholesome casual puzzle game! Create a trail of campfires and torches to make sure that no one is left alone under the cold starry night sky. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234830/extras/7afc72348794ae78c997193c7d261cc8.poster.avif?t=1741345311\" width=240 height=249 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234830/extras/7afc72348794ae78c997193c7d261cc8.webm?t=1741345311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234830/extras/b635ade8eca677e1de93d8272bdadff8.avif?t=1741345311\" width=320 height=427 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> No language barrier; apart from the title, the game does not include any text whatsoever for maximum inclusiveness :)<br></li><li> 80 levels of puzzlesolving fun, with additional level packs in the making<br></li><li> 3 different types of family members to be overjoyed by the presence of a nice warm fire - grandma, little brother & doggo, as well as the everfrosty snowman<br></li><li> 2 different ways of creating hotspots </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234830/extras/e0bc196601abd3a5833a644da02ead15.poster.avif?t=1741345311\" width=288 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234830/extras/e0bc196601abd3a5833a644da02ead15.webm?t=1741345311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234830/extras/b18e53e14a210a620fb993c424e207d3.avif?t=1741345311\" width=320 height=427 /></span>",
